+SatsangOUTR is a React 18 + Vite + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui website for a Satsang
+(spiritual community) student chapter at OUTR university. It was generated by Lovable.
+This task establishes the design system foundation — all other tasks build on top of it.
+
+Project root: `C:\Users\ASUS\Desktop\SatsangOUTR-main (1)\SatsangOUTR-main`
+
+## Files to Modify
+
+- `index.html` — add lang, meta description, Open Graph tags
+- `src/index.css` — completely rewrite CSS custom properties + Google Fonts import
+- `tailwind.config.ts` — update font families + extend color tokens
+- `src/assets/` — rename files with spaces to kebab-case
