+### Colors — EXACTLY 2 primary brand colors
+
+**Primary: Sacred Saffron Gold**
+- Base: `hsl(38, 93%, 41%)` → approx `#C8860A`
+- Light: `hsl(40, 85%, 55%)` → `#E8A832`
+- Lighter (tints): `hsl(42, 80%, 88%)` → `#F5E0B0`
+- Dark: `hsl(35, 90%, 28%)` → `#8A5808`
+
+**Secondary: Sacred Indigo**
+- Base: `hsl(215, 38%, 18%)` → approx `#1C2A3F`
+- Mid: `hsl(215, 35%, 22%)` → `#243447` (existing dark color, keep using)
+- Light: `hsl(215, 30%, 28%)` → `#2E4060`
+- Dark: `hsl(218, 45%, 10%)` → `#0D1620`
+
