+### Utility classes to keep/update in `src/index.css`:
+```css
+/* REPLACE the old saffron utilities — they were pointing at blue (HSL 200) */
+.text-gradient-gold {
+  @apply bg-clip-text text-transparent;
+  background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, hsl(var(--brand-primary)), hsl(var(--brand-primary-light)));
+}
+
+/* Keep old class name for backward compat but make it gold */
+.text-gradient-saffron {
+  @apply bg-clip-text text-transparent;
+  background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, hsl(var(--brand-primary)), hsl(var(--brand-primary-light)));
+}
+
+.bg-saffron-gradient {
+  background: linear-gradient(135deg, hsl(var(--brand-primary)), hsl(var(--brand-primary-dark)));
+}
+
+.bg-gold-gradient {
+  background: linear-gradient(135deg, hsl(var(--brand-primary)), hsl(var(--brand-primary-dark)));
+}
+
+.shadow-gold {
+  box-shadow: var(--gold-glow);
+}
+
+.border-gold {
+  border-color: hsl(var(--brand-primary) / 0.4);
+}
+
+/* Keep these for backward compat */
+.bg-saffron-light { background: hsl(var(--brand-primary-lighter)); }
+.bg-cream { background: hsl(42 60% 96%); }
+.shadow-saffron { box-shadow: var(--gold-glow); }
+.border-saffron { border-color: hsl(var(--brand-primary) / 0.3); }
+```
